.Dd May 2, 2010
.Dt AG_DRIVERWGL 3
.Os
.ds vT Agar API Reference
.ds oS Agar 1.4.1
.Sh NAME
.Nm AG_DriverWGL
.Nd agar WGL driver
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The Agar
.Va wgl
driver provides a direct interface to the Windows API, and renders
GUI elements using OpenGL primitives and textures.
On the Windows platform,
.Va wgl
is usually the default driver.
.Sh INHERITANCE HIERARCHY
.Xr AG_Driver 3 ->
.Xr AG_DriverMw 3 ->
.Nm .
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Bd -literal
AG_InitGraphics("wgl");
.Ed
.Sh OPTIONS
No driver options are currently defined.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr AG_Intro 3 ,
.Xr AG_Driver 3 ,
.Xr AG_DriverGLX 3 ,
.Xr AG_GL 3
.Bd -literal
http://www.opengl.org/
http://msdn.microsoft.com/
.Ed
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Va wgl
driver first appeared in Agar 1.4.0.
